data.description: This priced-to-sell property has a layout that is perfect for homeowners who want to customize and create their own unique vision. This home sits on approximately 0.17 acres and has three bedrooms with an additional office space and two bathrooms. When you arrive, you'll notice that the homestead is protected by a high chain-link fence with a remote access double gate and surrounded by mature oak trees providing ample shade areas. Inside, the unique 1600+sqft 1.5 story living space is cozy and provides comfortable seating that's conveniently located near the eat-in kitchen. The kitchen is designed with ample storage and prep space, making it perfect for any household chef. The primary suite can be used as a dedicated office space or a quaint reading nook. There is an extensive composite deck outside, along with a separate covered patio featuring handrailing and a ceiling fan, offering an ideal space for outdoor gatherings throughout the year. Additionally, there is a detached storage building on the property that measures 12'x14'. This building provides ample space for all your additional storage needs. This homestead is conveniently located near Medina Lake in the Pebble Beach subdivision making it the perfect retreat, VRBO or permanent residence.
